The second layer has a single green rectangular block positioned centrally on top of the cylinders. **3. Determine the Assembly Order:**

```json
{
  "Step1": "Move block with index 6",
  "Step2": "Move block with index 6",
```

**Explanation of Assembly Order:**

The base is built first by placing two identical cylindrical blocks (index 6). Then, the green block (index 1) is positioned on top, followed by the triangular block (index 11) on the green block.  The order is dictated by the physical stacking of the blocks, bottom to top.
